 This sketch takes an image and blast it into space. Nuff said.

 - Use the sliders to modify the image.
 - You can zoom in and rotate the image with the mouse
 - Note that the FILTERFACT slider will not have any effect
   if one the filters has not been activated : RED / BLUE / GREENFILTER
 - key s for exporting hi-res images [ once export is finished, program exits ].

